  ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE & MACHINE LEARNING
============================================================

Concept:     Transfer Learning
Category:    Technique
Definition:  Reuses pre-trained model weights for new related tasks
Year:        2009
Researchers: Pan and Yang survey
Applications:Fine-tuning LLMs, computer vision
Related:     Pre-training, fine-tuning, domain adaptation

Concept:     Constitutional AI
Category:    Alignment
Definition:  AI trained on principles via self-critique to reduce harm
Year:        2022
Researchers: Anthropic/Bai et al.
Applications:Claude safety and alignment
Related:     RLHF, harmlessness, helpfulness, honesty

Concept:     RAG
Category:    Architecture
Definition:  Combines retrieval from knowledge base with generative model
Year:        2020
Researchers: Lewis et al.
Applications:QA, chatbots, enterprise AI
Related:     Vector database, semantic search, LLM

